Text:
This was hard to find, figured I'd share the wealth...

Enjoy!!!!
Tim & Eric Awesome Show is broadcast in widescreen this season. It sucks that someone cut it to 4:3 as sides are missing (faces missing on people, there are half bodies and text missing...)
Or maybe it isn't being shown in widescreen, because the widescreen files as well as the 4:3 files all looked warped, wry and manipulated. What's going on with the aspect ratio this season...?

I'm having a hell of a time finding the rest of season 5 (episodes 4 and onwards).  
Any change those can get uploaded?
Thank you!
